    "steam_appid": 2192780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1770183731\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/eb25d229353c502dfd19e9b16e6f7473.webp?t=1770183731\" width=180 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场无尽怪物围攻中生存下来吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >消灭怪物，收集他们的眼睛，不断提升自己！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款Roguelite生存游戏中，你所能做的就是尽可能地生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集眼睛来提升当前的游戏回合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次游戏中积累积分，购买升级，帮助下一个幸存者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每次游戏都有独特的构建</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从各种升级中选择，创建每次游戏都独一无二且超强大的构建。你可以选择成为一个召唤者-无人机操作员，用无人机摧毁怪物，或者成为一个远程狙击手，使用电子子弹穿透敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/abcd55366c6dee958a965352bc4d3453.poster.avif?t=1770183731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/abcd55366c6dee958a965352bc4d3453.webm?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/abcd55366c6dee958a965352bc4d3453.mp4?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择你的英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从各种多样的角色和武器中选择，提供多种游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/50f8a4c0e2cd3e9ef3e01c6b2c2877bd.poster.avif?t=1770183731\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/50f8a4c0e2cd3e9ef3e01c6b2c2877bd.webm?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192780/extras/50f8a4c0e2cd3e9ef3e01c6b2c2877bd.mp4?t=1770183731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过30种不同的升级选择，每次游戏都有独特体验！</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多角色及其个性，发布后将有更多内容推出。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >适合忙碌玩家的休闲游戏，每次游戏仅需10-20分钟。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器、法球和物品系统帮助你变得更强大</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >未来计划的特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合作游戏。与朋友一起对抗成群结队的敌人</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP游戏。在MOBA风格的模式中与其他玩家对战</p></li></ul>",
